        "text": "I turned the aircraft on an easterly heading, pointing toward Gowen\nField, and had flown on that course for perhaps a minute when there suddenly\nappeared in the left hand portion of my field of vision an object which was\nblack and round."
      },
      "translation": {
        "text": "저는 항공기를 동쪽 방향으로 돌려 고웬 필드를 향했고, 그 항로로 약 1분간 비행했을 때 갑자기 제 시야의 왼쪽 부분에 검고 둥근 물체가 나타났습니다.",
